Types of pipelines: 

Declarative: Script is written withing hte pipeline box of jenkins. 
Example on my server: Declarative-test
Scripted: Pipeline job is written in jenkinsfile that is added to a repo
Example on my server: Multiplayer-game
-- Pipeline script from SCM
-- set to git
-- git url https://github.com/trainmefordevsecops/node-multiplayer-snake.git
--- no creds needed as this is a public repo
-- script path is set to Jenkinsfile
Pipelines are written in Groovy

note I have forked the project https://github.com/naughtron/node-multiplayer-snake.git